{"tid":1070721,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"鎖匙就鎖匙 鑰匙就鑰匙 乜撚野係鎖鑰","createTime":"2019-03-21T01:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T05:02:16.000Z","uid":51164,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"68f747e5df89069583659a439c5a115edbffeefd","tid":1070721,"uid":51164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:03:30.000Z","msg":"呢排身邊好多朋友都唔記得帶鎖匙出門口<br />\n<br />\n之後就會影張門口相 po ig 或者 snapchat 話自己冇門口入好慘<br />\n<br />\n但個caption 竟然係打<br />\n唔記得帶鎖鑰<br />\n<br />\n我心諗 乜撚野係鎖鑰 你唔記得帶條匙呀 個鎖咪裝左係度門到<br />\n<br />\n自問都讀過下書<br />\n<br />\n鎖同鑰都應該係講梗同一樣野<br />\n<br />\n見到身邊朋友口講正字正音 但係中文水平咁差 真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n鑰 讀音 joek6 係讀 藥<br />\n鎖鑰係解邊防要地 或者件事嘅闗鍵"},{"pid":"46c109902860891a35567938ffa9e634456e5b4a","tid":1070721,"uid":186844,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:16:21.000Z","msg":"闗 第一次見人打呢個 原來同關一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d0148f201fe9277a6aab3056affa6beeb0f745","tid":1070721,"uid":51164,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46c109902860891a35567938ffa9e634456e5b4a","tid":1070721,"uid":186844,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:16:21.000Z","msg":"闗 第一次見人打呢個 原來同關一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T02:15:46.000Z","msg":"闗同關係異體字 <br />\n好似牀同床咁"},{"pid":"08f9e2930cf4d971d38bb6bf6d42311a6285bb89","tid":1070721,"uid":111517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T02:24:43.000Z","msg":"問過咁打既friend<br />\n佢話係iphone自動suggest 既word choice <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d3d5d452b1d41218ff3c7804f5a84fba53ef48","tid":1070721,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32d0148f201fe9277a6aab3056affa6beeb0f745","tid":1070721,"uid":51164,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46c109902860891a35567938ffa9e634456e5b4a","tid":1070721,"uid":186844,"like":4,"dislike":2,"scor